[workspace]
members = ["crates/just-trace", "crates/zer0k-elastic-scraper", "crates/zer0k-elastic-wrangler", "api"]
default-members = ["api"]
resolver = "2"

[workspace.dependencies]
color-eyre = "0.6.2"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
serde_json = "1.0.97"
thiserror = "1.0.40"
toml = "0.7.5"

[workspace.dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.26"
features = ["serde"]

[workspace.dependencies.clap]
version = "4.3.8"
features = ["derive"]

[workspace.dependencies.gokz_rs]
version = "0.21"

[workspace.dependencies.sqlx]

version = "0.3.22"

[workspace.dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
